content:
Apply global branding to Vlocity Cards by using the Newport Design System. This system enables you to download, edit, and override existing CSS styles with your own.

Available beginning with Vlocity Insurance and Health Summer '19 and CME Fall '19.

Before You Begin:
Ensure Node and NPM are installed.
Clone the latest Newport Design System package from GitHub.
Edit the CSS in a local text editor and save changes.
Preview changes using Storybook.
Deploy Card Template Changes with the Newport Design System.
title: Apply Global Branding to Vlocity Cards
